            let rows.s0.y.loop_extent = ((rows.s0.y.max + 1) - rows.s0.y.min)
            let rows.s0.x.loop_max = rows.s0.x.max
            let rows.s0.x.loop_min = rows.s0.x.min
            let rows.s0.x.loop_extent = ((rows.s0.x.max + 1) - rows.s0.x.min)
            let rows.s0.x.x.loop_extent = (((rows.s0.x.loop_max - rows.s0.x.loop_min) + 64)/64)
            let rows.s0.x.x.loop_max = ((((rows.s0.x.loop_max - rows.s0.x.loop_min) + 64)/64) - 1)
            let rows.s0.x.x.loop_min = 0
            let rows.s0.x.v19.loop_extent = 64
            let rows.s0.x.v19.loop_max = (64 - 1)
            let rows.s0.x.v19.loop_min = 0
            for (rows.s0.y, rows.s0.y.loop_min, rows.s0.y.loop_extent) {
              for (rows.s0.x.x, rows.s0.x.x.loop_min, rows.s0.x.x.loop_extent) {
                let rows.s0.x.v19.base = ((rows.s0.x.x*64) + rows.s0.x.loop_min)
                vectorized (rows.s0.x.v19, rows.s0.x.v19.loop_min, rows.s0.x.v19.loop_extent) {
                  let rows.s0.x = (rows.s0.x.v19.base + rows.s0.x.v19)
                  rows((rows.s0.x.v19.base + rows.s0.x.v19), rows.s0.y) = (let t3 = (rows.s0.x.v19.base + rows.s0.x.v19) in ((int16(input(t3, (rows.s0.y - 1))) + ((int16)2*int16(input(t3, rows.s0.y)))) + int16(input(t3, (rows.s0.y + 1)))))
                }
              }
            }
          }
          consume rows {
            for (output.s0.x.x, output.s0.x.x.loop_min, output.s0.x.x.loop_extent) {
              let output.s0.x.v16.base = ((output.s0.x.x*64) + output.s0.x.loop_min)
              vectorized (output.s0.x.v16, output.s0.x.v16.loop_min, output.s0.x.v16.loop_extent) {
                let output.s0.x = (output.s0.x.v16.base + output.s0.x.v16)
                output((output.s0.x.v16.base + output.s0.x.v16), (output.s0.y.yi.base + output.s0.y.yi)) = (let t0 = (output.s0.y.yi.base + output.s0.y.yi) in (let t1 = (output.s0.x.v16.base + output.s0.x.v16) in uint8(shift_right((((rows((t1 - 1), t0) + ((int16)2*rows(t1, t0))) + rows((t1 + 1), t0)) + (int16)8), (int16)4))))
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

      prefetch(input, ((((input.stride.1/64)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + 7))*64) + -1), ((((output.extent.0 + 63)/64)*64) + 64), 1, 6, input.stride.1)
      for (output.s0.y.yi, 0, 4) {
        allocate rows[int16 * (((output.extent.0 + 127)/64)*64) * 1]
        produce rows {
          let rows.s0.y = ((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi)
          for (rows.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 127)/64)) {
            vectorized (rows.s0.x.v19, 0, 64) {
              rows[(((((output.extent.0 + 127)/64)*(rows.s0.y - ((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi)))*64) + ((rows.s0.x.x*64) + rows.s0.x.v19))] = (((int16(input[(((((input.stride.1/64)*rows.s0.y)*64) + ((rows.s0.x.x*64) + rows.s0.x.v19)) + -1)])*(int16)2) + int16(input[(((((input.stride.1/64)*(rows.s0.y + -1))*64) + ((rows.s0.x.x*64) + rows.s0.x.v19)) + -1)])) + int16(input[(((((input.stride.1/64)*(rows.s0.y + 1))*64) + ((rows.s0.x.x*64) + rows.s0.x.v19)) + -1)]))
            }
          }
        }
        consume rows {
          for (output.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 63)/64)) {
            vectorized (output.s0.x.v16, 0, 64) {
              output[((((output.stride.1/64)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi))*64) + ((output.s0.x.x*64) + output.s0.x.v16))] = uint8((((rows[(((output.s0.x.x*64) + output.s0.x.v16) + 2)] + (rows[((output.s0.x.x*64) + output.s0.x.v16)] + (rows[(((output.s0.x.x*64) + output.s0.x.v16) + 1)]*(int16)2))) + (int16)8)/(int16)16))
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

        produce rows {
          for (rows.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 127)/64)) {
            rows[ramp((rows.s0.x.x*64), 1, 64)] = halide.hexagon.interleave.vh(halide.hexagon.acc_add_2mpy.vh.vub.vub.b.b(halide.hexagon.zxt.vub(input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/64)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + 1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*64) + -1), 1, 64)]), input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/64)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi)) + rows.s0.x.x)*64) + -1), 1, 64)], input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/64)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + -1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*64) + -1), 1, 64)], (int8)2, (int8)1))
          }
        }
        consume rows {
          let t22 = ((output.stride.1/64)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi))
          if ((0 < output.extent.0)) {
            allocate c1[int16 * 64] in Stack
            c1[ramp(0, 1, 32)] = rows[ramp(0, 1, 32)]
            for (output.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 63)/64)) {
              c1[ramp(32, 1, 32)] = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*64) + 64), 1, 32)]
              output[ramp(((output.s0.x.x + t22)*64), 1, 64)] = (let t26 = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*64) + 32), 1, 32)] in (let t27.s = c1[ramp(0, 1, 32)] in (let t28.s = c1[ramp(32, 1, 32)] in halide.hexagon.pack.vh((((concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 2, 1, 32), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 2, 1, 32)) + halide.hexagon.add_mul.vh.vh.b(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 1, 1, 32), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 1, 1, 32)), (int8)2)) + x64((int16)8))/x64((int16)16))))))
              c1[ramp(0, 1, 32)] = c1[ramp(32, 1, 32)]
            }
          }
        }
        free rows
      }
    }
  }
}

  ret i32 %retval.3

        let rows.y.min_realized = min((output.s0.y.yi + output.s0.y.yi.base), rows.s0.y.min)

          produce rows {

            let rows.s0.y.loop_min = rows.s0.y.min

                }
              }
            }
          }
          consume rows {
            for (output.s0.x.x, output.s0.x.x.loop_min, output.s0.x.x.loop_extent) {

              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

            rows[ramp((rows.s0.x.x*128), 1, 128)] = (((int16x128(input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)])*x128((int16)2)) + int16x128(input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + -1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)])) + int16x128(input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + 1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)]))
          }
        }
        consume rows {
          let t22 = ((output.stride.1/128)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi))
          if ((0 < output.extent.0)) {
            allocate c1[int16 * 128] in Stack
            c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] = rows[ramp(0, 1, 64)]
            for (output.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 127)/128)) {
              c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)] = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*128) + 128), 1, 64)]
              output[ramp(((output.s0.x.x + t22)*128), 1, 128)] = (let t26 = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*128) + 64), 1, 64)] in (let t27.s = c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] in (let t28.s = c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)] in uint8x128((((concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 2, 1, 64), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 2, 1, 64)) + ((concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 1, 1, 64), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 1, 1, 64))*x128((int16)2)) + concat_vectors(t27.s, t26))) + x128((int16)8))/x128((int16)16))))))
              c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] = c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)]
            }
          }
        }
        free rows
      }
    }
  }
}

  for<Hexagon> (output.s0.__outermost, 0, 1) {
    for (output.s0.y.y, 0, ((output.extent.1 + 3)/4)) {
      prefetch(input, ((((input.stride.1/128)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + 7))*128) + -1), ((((output.extent.0 + 127)/128)*128) + 128), 1, 6, input.stride.1)
      for (output.s0.y.yi, 0, 4) {
        allocate rows[int16 * (((output.extent.0 + 255)/128)*128) * 1]
        produce rows {
          for (rows.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 255)/128)) {
            rows[ramp((rows.s0.x.x*128), 1, 128)] = halide.hexagon.interleave.vh(halide.hexagon.acc_add_2mpy.vh.vub.vub.b.b(halide.hexagon.zxt.vub(input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + 1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)]), input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)], input[ramp((((((input.stride.1/128)*(((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi) + -1)) + rows.s0.x.x)*128) + -1), 1, 128)], (int8)2, (int8)1))
          }
        }
        consume rows {
          let t22 = ((output.stride.1/128)*((output.s0.y.y*4) + output.s0.y.yi))
          if ((0 < output.extent.0)) {
            allocate c1[int16 * 128] in Stack
            c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] = rows[ramp(0, 1, 64)]
            for (output.s0.x.x, 0, ((output.extent.0 + 127)/128)) {
              c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)] = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*128) + 128), 1, 64)]
              output[ramp(((output.s0.x.x + t22)*128), 1, 128)] = (let t26 = rows[ramp(((output.s0.x.x*128) + 64), 1, 64)] in (let t27.s = c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] in (let t28.s = c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)] in halide.hexagon.pack.vh((((concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 2, 1, 64), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 2, 1, 64)) + halide.hexagon.add_mul.vh.vh.b(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), concat_vectors(slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t27.s, t26), 1, 1, 64), slice_vectors(concat_vectors(t26, t28.s), 1, 1, 64)), (int8)2)) + x128((int16)8))/x128((int16)16))))))
              c1[ramp(0, 1, 64)] = c1[ramp(64, 1, 64)]
            }
          }
        }
        free rows
      }
    }
  }

  %3 = getelementptr i8*, i8** %0, i32 1
  %4 = bitcast i8** %3 to %struct.halide_buffer_t**
  %5 = load %struct.halide_buffer_t*, %struct.halide_buffer_t** %4, align 4
  %6 = tail call i32 @gaussian3x3_hvx128(%struct.halide_buffer_t* %2, %struct.halide_buffer_t* %5) #13
  ret i32 0
}

; Function Attrs: norecurse nounwind readnone

entry:
  ret %struct.halide_filter_metadata_t* @gaussian3x3_hvx128_metadata_storage
}
